%N A015491 Inverse of 1482nd cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015491 Periodic with period length 1482. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015491 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015491/b015491.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015491 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1482.
